
---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Browse all registered grocery and clothing shops
- ✅ Register & Login using secure token authentication
- ✅ View shop details (name, category, contact, image)
- ✅ Add & view ratings and reviews
- ✅ Save favorite shops to your profile
- ✅ Search shops by name, category, or location
- ✅ Open shop addresses directly in Google Maps

---

## 🧪 Getting Started

### 🐍 Backend (Django)
```bash
cd backend
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
